  @api sr:renderBody(_, w, h, dispatch)  @ 482
  @api sr:renderStatusBar(_)  @ 590
  @api sr:closeTransients()  @ 600
      @contract  clear ephemeral preview/rename/drag state; the controller calls this on unbind
  @api sr:focusState()  @ 607
      @contract  acceptCmds is also blocked by ImGui.IsAnyItemActive (e.g. an InputInt being edited) so trim-field typing doesn't trigger commands

